title: Hillman 122048 Plate Hangers 5-1/2"-8" with Tip Protectors, 1
description: Hillman Plate Hangers secure decorative plates on walls. Ideal for drywall and plaster walls this hanger will ensure that your wall hanging project looks great. Includes 30 lb. Hillman professional brass picture hanger. Weight ratings are based on hangers nailed into studs.
